{"task":"translate","language":"english","duration":60.0,"text":"There is a general formula. There is a formula that is equivalent to the rate of death and the rate of infection. So, in order to become a pandemic, you have no choice but to kill too many hostages, and you have to balance it appropriately so that you can get out of the hostages. It has to be not too strong, but it has to be contagious. That's why it's the golden ratio of the corona formula. The contagious rate is determined according to the golden ratio. Is there a genetic difference between Spanish and Italian scientists? I think there is. Recently, a Spanish and Italian scientist published a paper. There is a genetic difference. So, until then, no one was sure of the difference in human genes. Because there is no data. But recently, it came out like that. We also studied it recently. We analyzed the genome of thousands of Koreans from the 10,000-person genome project in Ulsan. The initial study showed that Koreans may be a little resistant to the coronavirus.","segments":[{"id":0,"seek":0,"start":1.0,"end":3.0,"text":" There is a general formula.","tokens":[50414,821,307,257,2674,8513,13,50514],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.6791790723800659,"compression_ratio":1.8433735370635986,"no_speech_prob":0.8022136092185974},{"id":1,"seek":0,"start":3.0,"end":7.0,"text":" There is a formula that is equivalent to the rate of death and the rate of infection.","tokens":[50514,821,307,257,8513,300,307,10344,281,264,3314,295,2966,293,264,3314,295,11764,13,50714],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.6791790723800659,"compression_ratio":1.8433735370635986,"no_speech_prob":0.8022136092185974},{"id":2,"seek":0,"start":7.0,"end":11.0,"text":" So, in order to become a pandemic, you have no choice but to kill too many hostages,","tokens":[50714,407,11,294,1668,281,1813,257,5388,11,291,362,572,3922,457,281,1961,886,867,3975,64,2880,11,50914],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.6791790723800659,"compression_ratio":1.8433